<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{% if title %}{{ title }} · {% endif %}{{ site.title }}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta name="keywords" content="금융, 재테크, 증시, 투자 인사이트, 데일리 뉴스" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="{{ site.url }}" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nanum+Gothic:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="{{ site.description }}" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="{{ site.url }}" />
  <meta property="og:site_name" content="{{ site.title }}" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:site" content="@martin" />
  <style>
    :root {
      font-family: 'Nanum Gothic', 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f5ef;
      color: #0c1024;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #f7f5ef;
    }
    .app-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 40px 24px 60px;
    }
    header {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .tagline {
      color: rgba(12,16,36,0.65);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    nav a {
      color: #0c1024;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .hero {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .hero strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #0c1024;
    }
    .hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: rgba(12,16,36,0.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .layout-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(260px, 1fr);
      gap: 36px;
    }
    .issue-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
    }
    .issue-card h3 { margin-top: 12px; font-size: 1.7rem; }
    .issue-card p { line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(12,16,36,0.82); }
    .issue-meta, .issue-source {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(12,16,36,0.55);
    }
    .tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top:14px; }
    .tag {
      background: rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #1a213b;
    }
    .ad-slot {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
      padding: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(12,16,36,0.08);
    }
    .ad-slot strong { font-weight: 600; }
    .privacy-links a { color: #565b67; text-decoration: none; }
    footer {
      margin-top: 64px;
      padding-top: 24px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(12,16,36,0.12);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: rgba(12,16,36,0.6);
    }
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .layout-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      nav { justify-content: flex-start; }
      header { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "NewsMediaOrganization",
      "name": "{{ site.title }}",
      "url": "{{ site.url }}",
      "description": "{{ site.description }}",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "{{ site.title }}"
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-shell">
    <header>
      <div>
        <h1>{{ site.title }}</h1>
        <p class="tagline">{{ site.description }}</p>
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="Quick links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}">홈</a>
        <a href="mailto:martin@example.com">문의</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">프라이버시</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="hero">
      <div>
        <strong>Daily Market Digest</strong>
        <p>매일 새벽 청정한 관점으로 정리하는 글로벌 금리 · 통화 · 기술 흐름.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>AdSense-ready</strong>
        <p>사이드바 광고만으로도 방해가 없게 설계해, 수익화와 콘텐츠 집중을 동시에 지향합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <strong>Insight-first</strong>
        <p>핵심 요약 → 시장 영향 → 투자자 체크리스트로 구조화해 빠른 해석이 가능합니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="layout-grid">
      <main>
        {{ content | safe }}
      </main>
      <aside>
        <div class="ad-slot" aria-label="AdSense slot">
          <span>광고 슬롯</span>
          <strong>300x250·Responsive</strong>
          <p>네이버 블로그 스타일의 미니멀한 트래픽에도 어울리는 위치입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <section aria-labelledby="why-updated">
          <h3 id="why-updated">Daily signal tracker</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>매일 오전 06:00 KST 글로벌 데이터 체크</li>
            <li>금리 · 정책 · 원자재 · 기업 실적 테마를 태그로 분류</li>
            <li>Cloudflare build webhook → 자동 알림</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </aside>
    </div>
    <footer>
      <div>
        © {{ today.now | year }} {{ site.author }} · Cloudflare Pages · Eleventy
      </div>
      <div class="privacy-links">
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="{{ site.url }}/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
